author: etnu
msg: Created an optional short circuit for performing encoding detection. This makes a huge difference in CPU usage when dealing with large numbers of responses that do not specify their encoding. The biggest gains are found when using the optional flag that skips ICU, though if remote sites frequently fail to return Content-Type headers and are not either UTF-8 or ISO-8859-1, the result will be garbage.
